OL,3,CAndoni Iraola arrives on Merseyside to
OL,4,Cfinalise Liverpool deal
OL,6,FAndoni Iraola has arrived on
OL,7,FMerseyside to finalise the details on
OL,8,Fhis appointment as Liverpool's new
OL,9,Fhead coach.
OL,11,FHe is understood to have agreed a two-
OL,12,Fyear deal to succeed Arne Slot, who
OL,13,Fwas surprisingly sacked on at the end
OL,14,Fof May.
OL,16,FIraola, 43, flew into Liverpool John
OL,17,FLennon Airport on a private jet from
OL,18,FSan Sebastian in Spain, and was driven
OL,19,Faway in a silver people carrier on 4
OL,20,FJune.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
