OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1780607468
OL,3,CAndoni Iraola arrives on Merseyside to
OL,4,Cfinalise Liverpool deal
OL,6,FThe former Bournemouth manager was
OL,7,Fquickly identified as the club's
OL,8,Fprimary target as he was out of a
OL,9,Fcontract, having guided the Cherries
OL,10,Fto sixth place in the Premier League
OL,11,Fand their first European campaign.
OL,13,FThe Spaniard already had a
OL,14,Frelationship with Liverpool's sporting
OL,15,Fdirector Richard Hughes, since he
OL,16,Fappointed Iraola for the Cherries
OL,17,Fthree years ago.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
