PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1780607468
OL,3,CAndoni Iraola arrives on Merseyside to
OL,4,Cfinalise Liverpool deal
OL,6,FIt is understood Iraola wants to bring
OL,7,Fassistants Tommy Elphick and Shaun
OL,8,FCooper, analyst Tom Webber and fitness
OL,9,Fcoach Pablo de la Torre with him to
OL,10,FMerseyside.
OL,12,FFormer Liverpool players Thiago
OL,13,FAlcantara and the recently-retired
OL,14,FJames Milner have been linked with
OL,15,Fcoaching roles, but the make-up of the
OL,16,Fbackroom staff will remain a decision
OL,17,Ffor Iraola.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
