CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1780607468
OL,3,CAndoni Iraola arrives on Merseyside to
OL,4,Cfinalise Liverpool deal
OL,6,FThe appointment is in line with the
OL,7,Fclub's desire to move back towards a
OL,8,Fmore aggressive, front-foot, urgent
OL,9,Fstyle of football which they lost
OL,10,Fduring Slot's second season and which
OL,11,Fultimately cost him his job.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
